  "texts": [
    "When GPT-4 'receives' the human's language, it processes the text based on learned patterns and statistical relationships in its training data.",
    "However, this processing lacks true understanding.",
    "GPT-4 does not perceive or comprehend language in the human sense; it does not experience the meaning behind words or grasp the full context in which they are used.",
    "It 'mirrors' the language based on its programming and training, but without the grounding or experiential context that human understanding relies upon.",
    "The human listener perceives GPT-4's output and interprets it based on their own understanding and grounding."
  ],
